description:
Now in Japan, Eve is forced to make her way alone, far from the world she`s known. But before she can even settle in, she`s already found herself challenged to a tough match of golf!
Source: Crunchyroll

titles.title: Ichina Saotome Wants to Be a Pro Caddy!
Saotome Ichina wa Pro Caddie o Mezashiteru
早乙女イチナはプロキャディーを目指してる
